'''太阳制药'''（Sun Pharmaceutical Industries Limited；[[商业名称|商业名称]]：Sun Pharma）是总部位于印度[[孟买|孟买]]的一家跨国制药公司，主要在印度和美国生产销售各种制药配方和[[原料药|原料药]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/snapshot/snapshot.asp?ticker=SUNP:IN|title=SUN PHARMACEUTICAL INDUS (SUNP:National Stock Exchange of India): Stock Quote & Company Profile – Businessweek|work=Businessweek.com|accessdate=2 July 2015|archive-date=2014-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823144710/http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/snapshot/snapshot.asp?ticker=SUNP:IN|dead-url=no}}</ref>

它成立于1983年，2014年收购[[兰伯西|兰伯西]]，因此成为印度最大的制药公司。其72%的市场均位于国外，其中美国是最大市场，公司一半的营业额都来自美国。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sunpharma.com/sites/all/themes/sunpharma/images/annual/SPIL%20Feb14%20IR%20Presentation.pdf |title=Archived copy |access-date=10 April 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413142558/http://www.sunpharma.com/sites/all/themes/sunpharma/images/annual/SPIL%20Feb14%20IR%20Presentation.pdf |archive-date=2014-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

